text: Zohreh (Persian: زهره, Arabic:الزهرة) is a Persian female given name which means "Venus". This is a unique name (not in the top 1000 newborn names in the US in 2021). == People == * Zohreh Jooya * Zohreh Mojabi * Zohreh Sefati * Zohreh Tabibzadeh-Nouri == Related pages == * Zohreh, a proposed state-owned communications satellite that was not built. * Zahreh, a city in and the capital of Cham Khalaf-e Isa District, in Hendijan County, Khuzestan Province, Iran, also sometimes romanized Zohreh == References == Category:Disambiguation pages Category:Given names
